0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0744c44a1aae423fef1892dc5991fed04998b48d","tid":742642,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95e3798afe5158d9f9c82ee9f7ec1b9a49387daa","tid":742642,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:24:38.000Z","msg":"其實巴士司機值更高人工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:28:18.000Z","msg":"其實上面張圖 有第二個意思 。唔只巴士司機 你其他工都係成班俾人剝削緊 如果有人帶頭抵抗？我好肯定無人跟 仲借背後插果條友一刀"},{"pid":"669c6e4d70ccef1171e33dc37ea3737ab75cafc1","tid":742642,"uid":89801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:31:45.000Z","msg":"巴士佬新入職有2萬5 係計哂全部bonus同OT先有機會去到<br />\n事實上人工只有1萬中"},{"pid":"6a8cfe1607c3fcb47d75cac7f75008d6626bde1a","tid":742642,"uid":193407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:32:31.000Z","msg":"巴士司機救唔到人 淨係可以整死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb19f5b7b8ad8e07b51d4ddc1cd57d79bcb88580","tid":742642,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a8cfe1607c3fcb47d75cac7f75008d6626bde1a","tid":742642,"uid":193407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:32:31.000Z","msg":"巴士司機救唔到人 淨係可以整死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:36:16.000Z","msg":"巴士司機平安送你去目的地仲唔夠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗諗下其實醫生都唔係免我哋一死<br />\n只係推遲我們的死亡時間<br />\n而我們活耐咗可能更痛苦（所以先有安樂死訴求）"},{"pid":"2361752074f5944cd4ebbb96439cb294b4c502cf","tid":742642,"uid":179547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"供求問題<br />\n<br />\n再講白啲就係醫生門檻高，但又不可或缺，所以人工高，巴士司機大部分人受訓後都可以勝任，容易被取代，唔通真係關救人事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7441aee50f0cd7ef67d73d788dbd399995400706","tid":742642,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2361752074f5944cd4ebbb96439cb294b4c502cf","tid":742642,"uid":179547,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"供求問題<br />\n<br />\n再講白啲就係醫生門檻高，但又不可或缺，所以人工高，巴士司機大部分人受訓後都可以勝任，容易被取代，唔通真係關救人事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b437984a981c32c83beb7a99515e40224ce5a1c","tid":742642,"uid":193407,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb19f5b7b8ad8e07b51d4ddc1cd57d79bcb88580","tid":742642,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a8cfe1607c3fcb47d75cac7f75008d6626bde1a","tid":742642,"uid":193407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:32:31.000Z","msg":"巴士司機救唔到人 淨係可以整死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:36:16.000Z","msg":"巴士司機平安送你去目的地仲唔夠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗諗下其實醫生都唔係免我哋一死<br />\n只係推遲我們的死亡時間<br />\n而我們活耐咗可能更痛苦（所以先有安樂死訴求）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:44:28.000Z","msg":"平安送你去目的地基本野嚟咖喎 點解扭曲到變咗唔整死你已經要謝天謝地咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 照你咁講我去食嘢冇被人落藥係咪就要感恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人點都會死咖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係推遲死亡時間 但呢個係長短嘅問題 (本身你就快死但醫生救咗你 令你可以幾十年後自然死) 好大分別咖<br />\n人生一定有痛苦 但相對一定會有開心嘅嘢同幸福嘅嘢<br />\nBtw 巴打你經歷咗啲乜 點解可以扭曲成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ddb093300c44c177685b0f867cc88a83acd416","tid":742642,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:41:14.000Z","msg":"巴士司機 有無限死某兩間大學畢業生先準係香港執業先?<br />\n<br />\n巴士你肯操 去學  係人都考得個牌<br />\n做醫生 你係外國醫到識飛 都要番黎考執業試<br />\n等於你出黎做野係外國十幾廿年  上到director /president   叫你去考會考先準係香港 做野"},{"pid":"9c8ce58c1a5d96b3e758cf73ac9f6b9e16213b05","tid":742642,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:43:01.000Z","msg":"要求唔同 冇得比"},{"pid":"9a21f0b804475ff8b3f832edc4c1696534058a8a","tid":742642,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T19:45:42.000Z","msg":"加拿大巴士司機唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ca60cb5f9b89908091ae47ae27d9982da5458e","tid":742642,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85cc08c2fde7f5fa6cad11bcd36dda9bf3f621bf","tid":742642,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T17:20:38.000Z","msg":"成日話醫生掌管人生死所以值咁高人工<br />\n計我話每日更多人性命交付俾巴士司機但點解只每月值二萬蚊<br />\n點解醫生成日犯錯又唔屌得<br />\n巴士司機無犯錯都要俾人出氣？<br />\n點解港女見到醫生會濕晒（話佢救急扶危）<br />\n又唔會見到巴士司機發情？<br />\n有無人解答到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T10:22:35.000Z","msg":"工程咪一撚樣。<br />\n工程質素 直接影響意外機會和社會衛生。<br />\n仲重要過醫療行業<br />\n<br />\n但人工........<br />\n<br />\n在經濟學上<br />\n唔存在因為你貢獻多少<br />\n影響你人工<br />\n只會因供應需求而調節<br />\n所以業主咩都唔做<br />\n佢月入會比你多好多"}]}